msg.msgText: The new EnableDiskPersistence value that is specified is the same as the current value.The value of EnableDiskPersistence is not changed. The CleanStore process is not run.

msgExplanation.p: No operation is performed because the new value of EnableDiskPersistence is the same as the current value.

msgUserResponse.p: Ensure that the specified value for EnableDiskPersistence is valid.
